The article "IPL 2011 Today’s Match: Kochi  
Tuskers vs Mumbai Indians" has been copied by the infringing blog starting  
with text "
Kochi tuskers Kerala vs Mumbai Indians IPL 2011 to days match. Kochi  
looking for first victory in 3 matches. Check the article to get updates  
and Live scores of the Kochi Tuskers vs Mumbai Indians match


IPL 2011 Today's Match: Kochi Tuskers vs Mumbai Indians

I t is Vishu in Kerala; everyone expects a cracker of Performance form he  
home team Kochi Tuskers Kerala against the Mumbai Indians. Kochi Tuskers  
lost their previous two matches; they are the only team yet to register a  
win in this IPL 2011. Kochi will have to face the champion side Mumbai  
Indians ; it will be difficult for Kochi to pull a win against Mumbai  
Indians who are looking favourites to win IPL 2011.

Kochi lost their last two matches against Pune warriors and RCB due to the  
Tactical errors at the death overs of the game. In both the games they had  
an edge over the opposition till the last two overs , the death overs still  
a concern for KTK, in the first game against RCB it was Raifi Gomez ruined  
KTK chances by giving away 20 odd runs, against Pune it was Murali over  
which turned things in favour of Pune." and continuing till end
